# Copy this file to ".env" (which is gitignored) and fill in the value.
# Never commit the real secret — this repo is public.

# Google Analytics 4 Measurement Protocol API secret.
# Create it at: GA4 Admin → Data streams → (your stream) →
#   Measurement Protocol API secrets → Create.
# It is NOT the Measurement ID (G-XXXX) or Stream ID.
# Leave empty to keep analytics disabled (its network path is dead-code-removed).
GA_API_SECRET=
